<div class="title">Best Friend, Worst Enemy</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam (Xanax)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Ralph+Lauren&Exact=1">Ralph Lauren</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Ralph Lauren. "Best Friend, Worst Enemy: An Experience with Alprazolam (Xanax) (exp75798)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 9, 2009. erowid.org/exp/75798</div>

<br/>



